SmugmugTransport - a lightweight ruby interface for the SmugMug API

HOWTO: 
-----

1. Define SMUGMUG_API_KEY in your rails project
2. Copy this plugin into vendor/plugins
3. Go to your project root and test it with 
   rake smugmug_transport_test:auth 
      and
   rake smugmug_transport_test:import
4. Look at the rake tasks as examples, and integrate into your sauce 